                   throws java.lang.IllegalArgumentException
        Creates a new instance of a pending transaction with the given parameters.
        Parameters:
        transactionId - the identifier of the transaction.
        message - the context message sent in the push notification.
        postbackUri - the location of the endpoint to complete the transaction operation.
        subType - the specific sub type of this authentication method.
        dataToSign - the value to be signed the private key created for the enrolled signature method.
        signatureMethodKeyName - the name of the key to be used for this transaction.
        createdOn - the timestamp in UTC when the transaction was created on the server
        additionalData - additional contextual attributes.
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if any argument is null.
        Since:
        2.0.3
